  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.5">
<l>viṇṭāṉ viṇpuka veñcamat tariyāyp pariyōṉ mārvakam paṟṟi<supplied>p</supplied>pi  ḷantu</l>
<l>paṇṭā ṉuyyavōr mālvarai yēntum paṇpā ḷāpara ṉēpavit tiraṉē</l>
<l>kaṇṭēṉ nāṉkali yukattataṉ taṉmai karuma māvatu meṉṟaṉak kaṟintēṉ,</l>
<l>aṇṭā niṉṉaṭi yaṉṟimaṟ ṟaṟiyē ṉaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of fine character who bore a dark mountain long ago</l>
<l rend="indent">so the cows were saved,</l>
<l>Having seized the stout one, cleaving his broad chest as a lion in heated battle,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that adversary entered heaven,</l>
<l>Divine one, pure one, I saw the nature of the Kali Yuga;</l>
<l rend="indent">I knew it would be karma for me.</l>
<l>[Lord of] the universe, besides your feet, I do not know any[thing] other,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
